fr.xephi.authme.datasource.mysqlextensions

Class MySqlExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.xephi.authme.datasource.mysqlextensions.MySqlExtension

  • public abstract class MySqlExtension
extends Object
    Extension for the MySQL data source for forums. For certain password hashes (e.g. phpBB), we want to hook into the forum board and execute some actions specific to the forum software.
